BT /F1 10 Tf 50 750 Td 14 TL () Tj T* (Todo jogo Lua usa funcoes globais especiais:) Tj T* () Tj T* (function aegis_init\(\)) Tj T* (-- chamado quando a cena/script e carregado) Tj T* (end) Tj T* () Tj T* (function aegis_update\(dt\)) Tj T* (-- chamado a cada frame; dt em segundos) Tj T* (end) Tj T* () Tj T* (function aegis_draw\(\)) Tj T* (-- desenho manual opcional em coordenadas de mundo/camera) Tj T* (end) Tj T* () Tj T* (function aegis_draw_ui\(\)) Tj T* (-- desenho manual opcional sem transformacao de camera) Tj T* (end) Tj T* () Tj T* (Um `main.lua` tipico registra cenas e abre o menu:) Tj T* () Tj T* (GAME = { score = 0 }) Tj T* (local booted = false) Tj T* () Tj T* (function aegis_init\(\)) Tj T* (aegis.registerScene\("menu", "scenes/menu.lua"\)) Tj T* (aegis.registerScene\("game", "scenes/game.lua"\)) Tj T* (booted = false) Tj T* (end) Tj T* () Tj T* (function aegis_update\(dt\)) Tj T* (if not booted then) Tj T* (booted = true) Tj T* (aegis.transitionTo\("menu", "none", 0.01\)) Tj T* (end) Tj T* (end) Tj T* () Tj T* (function aegis_draw\(\) end) Tj T* () Tj T* () Tj T* (6. Cenas) Tj T* () Tj T* (Use `aegis.registerScene\(nome, caminho\)` para registrar uma cena e) Tj T* (`aegis.transitionTo\(nome, efeito, duracao\)` para trocar.) Tj T* () Tj T* (Exemplo:) Tj T* () Tj T* (aegis.registerScene\("win", "scenes/win.lua"\)) Tj T* ET
endstream
